" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足走甩都話唔應該張揚走佬方法<br />\n啲裝甲車水炮車好似無爛過咁，post都唔見多個<br />\n兩三個月前明明仲講緊水炮車一出全部都要走唔打得，而家側側膀都叫打贏左架水炮車都無人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:40:27.000Z","msg":"成個中聯辦成個黑警嘅心戰室出晒嚟帶風向<br />\n啲手足又覺得攻唔到入去好愧疚<br />\n所以咪畀人帶到風向囉<br />\n根本就要正視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:45:09.000Z","msg":"然後就會有人屌你咁都叫驘？<br />\n知唔知有幾多手足俾人斷正拉左<br />\n再下多句就繼續屌守城<br />\n<br />\n尋晚多左咁多和理非行得前左咁多又係無乜人講，雖然朝早無人係灰機，但夜晚果個人數都係超出哂想像（仲要好多真係企得幾前（而且一定係企得前過平時嘅佢地，因為好多都無乜心態準備同行動，呢點都唔知算好定差其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3abfceb480ce6b8156afc241f4cebc770f04128","tid":1739790,"uid":78132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86eaac4704854ba8dcc68c6bbf2a6aac64686af6","tid":1739790,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:30:37.000Z","msg":"游繩 , 水渠果啲係top勇武 , 仲有三四個位都走左唔少人 , 例如路軌都唔知走左幾多人啲狗先至發現 , 其實唔算捉到核心勇武"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:46:21.000Z","msg":"重有和理非開始踏入戰場<br />\n今日做物資 下次可以企前滅煙<br />\n最重要係踏出第一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地一直都諗唔到點做既野<br />\n班狗幫我地做左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過犧牲左好多手足先做到<br />\n希望和理非快d覺悟"},{"pid":"19723e1328f221790b585e4b1ef4159fa8ffe267","tid":1739790,"uid":256505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4d896a9a7da9fbe62ec06df367ad58439c61387","tid":1739790,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:18:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">就係因為黑警之前輸得太多<br />\n美國又準備立法</span></span><br />\n軍心潰散<br />\n先要all in一場去振奮軍心<br />\n<br />\n所以大家要堅持返之前戰略<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">be water</span></span><br />\n打遊擊戰打巷戰<br />\n<br />\n同埋多啲宣傳理大勇武嘅戰績<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">燒裝甲車根本就係同烏克蘭革命一樣咁勁</span></span><br />\n根本冇輸過<br />\n只係理大入面唔夠物資<br />\n同埋外面啲援軍唔夠武器咋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:48:02.000Z","msg":"借位，多圖又大又阻，唔好意思！<br />\n<br />\n近日勇武的手法已經開始漸漸失效，<br />\n特別係理大一役傷亡慘重，一眾抗爭者感到非常無力，到底有無咩係警暴同制度暴力底下，和理非可以做到？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">首先和理非絕對唔係沒有用，有很多方法我地都未完全運用到！<br />\n任何方法只要持之而行一定<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有效</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n請參考［非暴力抗爭小冊子］<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZT29FbC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZT29FbC.jpg&h=84a73ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u2vSCYf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu2vSCYf.jpg&h=cb844c17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b5BFMRz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb5BFMRz.jpg&h=ca8e331b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fBDH0bx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfBDH0bx.jpg&h=c64d81bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJcd6Rw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJcd6Rw.jpg&h=4b0aa756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PF8tbh9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPF8tbh9.jpg&h=9b28ef1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PbGuFbt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPbGuFbt.jpg&h=1ebff131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oG6Obh5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoG6Obh5.jpg&h=0e29ccd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Xvy6Rr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Xvy6Rr.jpg&h=a9cab006&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYSE2pK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYSE2pK.jpg&h=ade912bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UZafAN3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUZafAN3.jpg&h=a23fdcf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNzzRmn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNzzRmn.jpg&h=acf27469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AGLOVN0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAGLOVN0.jpg&h=1eb85f13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8tYdnsZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8tYdnsZ.jpg&h=344559b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XNvy6Ws.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNvy6Ws.jpg&h=199efcb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完整版如下，手足請留底+廣傳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">從知識面武裝化和理非</span>！<br />\nGene Sharp《從獨裁走向民主》（From Dictatorship to Democracy）<br />\n附件<a href=\"https://idemocracy.asia/sites/default/files/file/news/%E5%BE%9E%E7%8D%A8%E8%A3%81%E5%88%B0%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fidemocracy.asia%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Ffile%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25BE%259E%25E7%258D%25A8%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB.pdf&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=c6613c09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://idemocracy.asia/sites/default/files/file/news/%E5%BE%9E%E7%8D%A8%E8%A3%81%E5%88%B0%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">和理非絕對有好多野可以做！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">任何方法都要時間發揮效力，團結持之而行有耐性，不分化不割席。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>最後呼籲大家支持非暴力公民抗命，放棄勇武抗爭方式！<br />\n繼續Be water! 無大台！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同時停火到區選戰結束為止。</span><br />\n<br />\n讓大家好好冷靜，思考下一步！<br />\n祈禱埋大和營救手足安全回家。<br />\n<br />\n只要永不言敗，民主自由不死。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">求幫推爆+廣傳</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n原Post唔該入去推爆佢# <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/eyJDKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/eyJDKT</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc661cd2a19d3fa06feb62e64cdf40e6165d1d6d","tid":1739790,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:57:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7e4caec21eee0902c88dc97875a3b816d23ba7be","tid":1739790,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T18:14:55.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"440e4753ad7abc498109e6c5a3ce7bb21018f0d3","tid":1739790,"uid":96544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T18:29:26.000Z","msg":"講真其實而家班狗塞緊紅隧同尖東一帶<br />\n呢個時候如果有人塞埋東西隧一般市民都唔知點<br />\n千其唔好嘩做"},{"pid":"1088018ce0fccc8d1d7f378e67990fe0b8211b99","tid":1739790,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T18:32:28.000Z","msg":"鄧小強新官上任被制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2961d9f2d9b4274d051f8c8f173f8617ed8ad4","ti